BloomFilters
============

What is this?
-------------

This repository contains the implementation of a standard Bloom Filter and a
Blocked Bloom Filter. The two implementations are empirically compared using a
static dataset under varying numbers of hash functions, bits per entry, filter
sizes, and load factors.


Requirements
------------

* g++
* make
* python3
* python3-venv
* pip


Building
--------

To build the project:

	make build

To remove executables and experimental results:

	make clean


Testing
-------

To test the filter implementations:

	make test


Experiments
-----------

To run all experiments:

	make experiment


Project Layout
--------------

src/
	BloomFilter.cpp/.hpp      		- Standard Bloom Filter implementation
	BlockedBloomFilter.cpp/.hpp 	- Blocked Bloom Filter implementation
	Experiments.cpp           		- Experiment driver
	plot.py                         - Plots experimental results

tests/
	TestBloomFilter.cpp/.hpp        - Tests for Bloom Filter
	TestBlockedBloomFilter.cpp/.hpp - Tests for Blocked Bloom Filter

libs/
	xxhash.c/.h 					- xxHash library for hashing

data/
	data.txt						- Static dataset used in experiments
